title: Gigi Hadid
summary: Jelena Noura Hadid (born April 23, 1995) is an American model. In November 2014, she made her debut in the Top 50 Models ranking at Models.com.[5] In 2016, she was named International Model of the Year by the British Fashion Council.[6] Over the span of four years, Hadid has made thirty-five appearances on international Vogue magazine covers.[7]
